OL,5, A drink-driver who ploughed into a     
OL,6, crowd of pedestrians outside a         
OL,7, takeaway, fatally injuring a student,  
OL,8, has been convicted of her murder.      
OL,10,FRebecca Steer, 22, died in hospital    
OL,11,Fafter the crash in Oswestry,           
OL,12,FShropshire, in October in which she was
OL,13,Fdragged under the killer's Volvo.      
OL,15,FStephen McHugh, who did not hold a     
OL,16,Flicence, admitted drinking and taking  
OL,17,Fdrugs before getting behind the wheel. 
OL,19,FMs Steer's family said they would      
OL,20,Falways feel "robbed" over her death.   
